Service_Navigation
robots: ServiceRobot
humans: Human_Assistant, Human_Supervisor
locations: serviceStartLocation, pickupZone, elevatorLocation, floorLocation, serviceGoalLocation
resources: objectToBeTransported, floorSelection: boolean, serviceCompletionConfirmation: boolean

ServiceRobot:
  1: moveTo serviceStartLocation
  2: moveTo pickupZone
  3: wait until objectToBeTransported in pickupZone
  4: pick objectToBeTransported
  5: moveTo elevatorLocation
  6: notify Human_Assistant at elevatorLocation
  7: receiveFrom Human_Assistant floorSelection
  8: moveTo floorLocation
  9: moveTo serviceGoalLocation
  10: deposit objectToBeTransported
  11: receiveFrom Human_Supervisor serviceCompletionConfirmation
